                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;After patch &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/980&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/980&lt;/a&gt; is landed, direct IO will bypass CLIO so it&apos;s not necessary to maintain CPT_TRANSIENT pages any more.&lt;/p&gt;

